# MEME Suite custom alphabet: Colorblind-safe palette
# Wong (2011) "Points of Significance: Color blindness" palette.
# Distinguishable under protanopia, deuteranopia, tritanopia.
# Usage:  meme --alph colorblind_dna.alph <sequences> ...
ALPHABET "DNA Colorblind-Safe" DNA-LIKE
A "Adenine" 009E73 ~ T "Thymine" D55E00
C "Cytosine" 0072B2 ~ G "Guanine" E69F00
# Ambiguous symbols
U = T
R = AG
Y = CT
K = GT
M = AC
S = CG
W = AT
B = CGT
D = GAT
H = ACT
V = ACG
N = ACGT
X = ACGT
